snippet.title: Basic Math - Rounding numbers
snippet.description: This video shows how to round numbers.  Remember to first identify the place value being rounded, and then to check the next lace value.  If it is 5 or more, round up.  If it is 4 or less round down.  For more videos visit http://www.mysecretmathtutor.com
